{"tid":2421154,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"溫哥華學生嘅 tg grp","createTime":"2021-02-24T10:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T22:12:01.000Z","uid":313719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"def9f47175e4aeb9d1ba7fd4f94e1cdbef2aeb5f","tid":2421154,"uid":313719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:18:14.000Z","msg":"因為武肺已經成年 而且見到愈黎愈多港人移民到溫哥華&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想開一個只係溫哥華學生嘅tg grp 比係溫<br />\n<br />\n哥華讀緊書嘅各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋都好歡迎黎左好耐 但係平時好摺又突然想<br />\n<br />\n識朋友嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲入黎一齊吹水 鳩up&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論鳩嘢 學術 移民 咩野都可以講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncovid之後仲可能會有聚&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打快啲入grp啦&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf1L-N5sXD1WLSPMzYHOWhTPloGHSLhnEO_Di_b7n4zWzGKig/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf1L-N5sXD1WLSPMzYHOWhTPloGHSLhnEO_Di_b7n4zWzGKig%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=f1396b41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/form